'''Claude Delbeke''' (born 1935) is a Belgian civil engineer (retired) and philatelist who signed the [[Roll of Distinguished Philatelists]] in 1997.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.academiebelgium.be/fiche.asp?id=1|title=Academie Belgium - Fiche|website=www.academiebelgium.be}}</ref> He is the [[Royal Philatelic Society of London]]'s representative for Belgium.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rpsl.org.uk/society_representatives.asp|title=The Royal Philatelic Society London|website=www.rpsl.org.uk}}</ref> The Medaille Claude Delbeke is awarded by the [[Académie Royale de Philatélie]] of Belgium of which Delbeke is the former president.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.academiebelgium.be/cd.asp|title=Academie Belgium -|website=www.academiebelgium.be}}</ref>
