'''Oscar d'Andrea''' is an [[Italy|Italian]] [[bobsled]]der who competed in the early 1970s. He won a silver medal in the four-man event at the [[FIBT World Championships 1971|1971 FIBT World Championships]] in [[Cervinia]].

